    public static class SwingObservables.ObservableAdjustmentListener
extends DefaultObservable<AdjustmentEvent>
implements AdjustmentListener
    The observable adjustment listener which relays adjustmentValueChanged() events to next(). This observable never signals finish() or error().
    Author:
    akarnokd, 2011.02.01.
